{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-js","path":"/xampp-pear","result":{"data":{"remark":{"fields":{"path":"xampp-pear"},"meta":{"title":""},"headings":[{"value":"XAMPP Pear"}],"html":"<h1>XAMPP Pear</h1>\n<p><strong>List installed packages</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">C:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>xampp<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>php<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>pear.bat list</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Install package with all dependencies</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">C:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>xampp<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>php<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>pear.bat <span class=\"token function\">install</span> PACKAGE <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-a</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Help</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">C:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>xampp<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>php<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>pear.bat <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">help</span> COMMAND</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Upgrade</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">C:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>xampp<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>php<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>pear.bat upgrade-all</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Channels</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.developertutorials.com/pear-manual/guide.users.commandline.channels.html\">Guide users commandline channels</a></p>\n<p><strong>PEAR.INI</strong></p>\n<p>Add <code class=\"language-text\">PHP_PEAR_SYSCONF_DIR</code> sys variable that point to phpâ€™s dir</p>\n<p><strong>BETA</strong></p>\n<p>To install beta use something like this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">pear <span class=\"token function\">install</span> channel://pear.php.net/PEAR_Frontend_Web-0.7.5</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Pear webinstaller</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">pear <span class=\"token function\">install</span> pear/PEAR<span class=\"token comment\">#webinstaller</span></code></pre></div>"}},"pageContext":{"id":"8eb0b3ee-40d6-5a3b-841f-964e7b02c5ea"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}